{"about_the_game":"<strong>Arcade Space Survivor</strong> is a minimal, arcade-style Action-Roguelike.<br>Fight against waves of different enemies.<br>Collect <strong>Exp</strong> to upgrade your spaceship.<br><br><strong>Arcade Space Survivor</strong> offers an innovative and unique gameplay experience in the existing action-roguelike genre.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944000/extras/gameplay_1.gif?t=1714554689\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Online Leaderboard<br></li><li>12 unique Upgrades with up to 37 levels (additional content planned)<br></li><li>15 different enemy types (additional content planned)<br></li><li>Gamemodes: Survival, Daily Run, Challenges<br></li><li>Point of Interests: capture zones, explosion zones (additional content planned)<br></li><li>Deadly meteors for player and enemies</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Special:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>No mouse required (<i>perfect for laptop</i>)<br></li><li>Perfect for controller</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Differences to other games of this genre:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Instead of <strong>HP</strong> the player has <strong>LIFES</strong> (<i>like in old arcade games</i>).<br></li><li><strong>Exp</strong> will disappear after a certain time (<i>10 seconds</i>).</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944000/extras/gameplay_3.gif?t=1714554689\" /><br><br>Game by: <i>Marvin Woelke</i> / <i>MAWO</i>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944000/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1714554689","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944000/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1714554689","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2944000/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1714554689","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstati